N2  - Peter Jackson and Ian Greaves describe a collaboration between LEO Pharma and the Gnosall Surgery in south west Staffordshire in which a nurse-led dermatology clinic, focusing on mild-to-moderate eczema, psoriasis and acne, was set up. This successful partnership resulted in reduced waiting lists, improved service quality and the development of a service template that could be used by other PCOs.
